msgid ""
"So, here's (finally) the complete list of all the <acronym>DCOP</acronym> "
"which &knewsticker; provides:"
msgstr ""
"Voici (pour finir) une liste complète de toutes les fonctions "
"<acronym>DCOP</acronym> que &knewsticker; fournit&nbsp;:"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid "updateNews"
msgstr "updateNews"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid ""
"This function forces &knewsticker; to updates the internal list of articles "
"(&eg; it queries the list of news sources which has been <link "
"linkend=\"config-newssources\">configured</link>"
" for new news) and downloads them when neccessary."
msgstr ""
"Cette fonction force &knewsticker; à mettre à jour sa liste d'articles "
"interne (&cad; qu'il interroge les serveurs de nouvelles <link "
"linkend=\"config-newssources\">configurés</link> dans sa liste et "
"télécharge les nouveaux articles si nécessaire."

#: index.docbook:910
msgid "This also works if &knewsticker; is currently in offline mode."
msgstr "Ceci fonctionne également si &knewsticker; est en mode déconnexion."

#: index.docbook:910
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Exemple&nbsp;:"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid "reparseConfig"
msgstr "reparseConfig"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid ""
"The <command>reparseConfig</command>"
" command makes &knewsticker; reload it's configuration from the "
"configuration file. This function is used by the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration\">configuration dialog</link> to talk to "
"&knewsticker; but you can use it in case you modified the configuration file "
"by hand."
msgstr ""
"La commande <command>reparseConfig</command>"
" fait en sorte que &knewsticker; recharge sa configuration depuis le fichier "
"de configuration. Cette fonction est utilisée par la <link "
"linkend=\"configuration\">boîte de dialogue de configuration</link> pour "
"demander communiquer avec &knewsticker;, mais vous pouvez l'utiliser au cas "
"où vous auriez modifié le fichier de configuration à la main."

#: index.docbook:910
msgid ""
"The configuration file is saved in "
"<filename>~/.kde/share/config/knewstickerrc</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Le fichier de configuration est sauvegardé dans "
"<filename>~/.kde/share/config/knewstickerrc</filename>"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>dcop</command> "
"<option>knewsticker</option> <option>KNewsTicker</option> "
"<option>reparseConfig</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>dcop</command> "
"<option>knewsticker</option> <option>KNewsTicker</option> "
"<option>reparseConfig</option></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid "setOfflineMode [bool]"
msgstr "setOfflineMode [bool]"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid ""
"You can call this function to define whether &knewsticker; is currently in "
"the offline mode (&eg; whether &knewsticker; should query the <link "
"linkend=\"config-newssources\">configured news sites</link> for new news)."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez appeler cette fonction pour définir si &knewsticker; est "
"actuellement en mode déconnexion ou non (&cad; si &knewsticker; doit "
"interroger les <link linkend=\"config-newssources\">sites de nouvelles "
"configurés</link> pour de nouveaux articles."

#: index.docbook:910
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>dcop</command> "
"<option>knewsticker</option> <option>KNewsTicker</option> "
"<option>setOfflineMode</option> <option>true</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>dcop</command> "
"<option>knewsticker</option> <option>KNewsTicker</option> "
"<option>setOfflineMode</option> <option>true</option></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid "to enable the offline mode, or type"
msgstr "pour activer le mode déconnexion, ou tapez"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>dcop</command> "
"<option>knewsticker</option> <option>KNewsTicker</option> "
"<option>setOfflineMode</option> <option>false</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>dcop</command> "
"<option>knewsticker</option> <option>KNewsTicker</option> "
"<option>setOfflineMode</option> <option>false</option></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:910
msgid "to disable offline mode."
msgstr "pour désactiver le mode déconnexion."
